    "explain": "This pair of invisible characters go on either side of glyphs to render them within a cartouche.",
    "explainsl": "nimi kalama li ni: ona li sama kute tawa nimi pi toki ante li nimi pi toki pona ala. 'sitelen Lasina' la 'Lasina' li nimi kalama. sitelen pona la nimi kalama ale li lon insa poki.",
    "explainsp": "nimi kalama li ni> zz ona li sama kute tawa nimi pi(toki ante) li nimi pi(toki+pona ala). sitelen open en sitelen pini li selo e poki.",

    "example-before": "jan 'cartouche start' anpa mama awen 'cartouche end'",
